      "components": [
        {
          "html": "<style>\n  :root {\n    --color-lumi-green: #107c10;\n    --color-rich-meadow: #054b16;\n    --color-electric-lime: #9bf00b;\n    --color-cyber-yellow: #ffd800;\n    --color-absolute-zero: #000000;\n    --color-snowfield-white: #ffffff;\n    --color-charcoal-depth: #333333;\n    --color-whisper-gray: #f2f2f2;\n    --color-dark-steel: #616161;\n    --color-onyx-shadow: #262626;\n    --font-segoe-ui: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;\n  }\n</style>\n<div style=\"width:600px;background:var(--color-lumi-green);font-family:var(--font-segoe-ui);padding:32px 36px 36px 36px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:12px;\">\n    <span style=\"background:var(--color-electric-lime);color:var(--color-rich-meadow);font-family:var(--font-segoe-ui);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.75px;padding:3px 8px;text-transform:uppercase;display:inline-block;\">XBOX GAME PASS</span>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"color:var(--color-snowfield-white);font-family:var(--font-segoe-ui);font-size:28px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.22;margin:0 0 12px 0;\">Descubre tu siguiente<br>juego favorito</h2>\n  <p style=\"color:var(--color-snowfield-white);font-family:var(--font-segoe-ui);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;margin:0 0 28px 0;max-width:420px;\">Nuevos juegos el mismo día de su lanzamiento. Cientos de juegos. Transmitid desde cualquier lugar. Ganad recompensas.</p>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:var(--color-electric-lime);color:var(--color-rich-meadow);font-family:var(--font-segoe-ui);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:0;letter-spacing:0.3px;\">\n      ÚNETE A GAME PASS\n      <svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M2 5h6M5 2l3 3-3 3\" stroke=\"#054b16\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/></svg>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;color:var(--color-snowfield-white);font-family:var(--font-segoe-ui);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.3px;\">\n      VER DETALLES\n      <svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M2 5h6M5 2l3 3-3 3\" stroke=\"#ffffff\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"square\"/></svg>\n    </a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
